org.processmining.plugins.ilpminer.templates.javailp

Class PetriNetSingleILPModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.processmining.plugins.ilpminer.ILPModelJavaILP
      • org.processmining.plugins.ilpminer.templates.javailp.PetriNetSingleILPModel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FewestArcsSingleILPModel, PetriNetSingleLPModel

    public class PetriNetSingleILPModel
extends ILPModelJavaILP
    Implements the abstract ILPModel class. Looks for a place for each causal dependency in the log, combined in one ILP problem.
    Author:
    T. van der Wiel

    • Field Detail

      • slackWeight

        public int slackWeight
        Should be as low as possible due to problems occuring in the solver when summations go over Integer.MAX_VALUE. Lower bound is: max trace length * number of transitions
